          <p class='first-para'>
            I need further help from the noble Lord&#x2014;partly because of the acoustics. Is he saying that we should add to the shopping list of bodies to whom the restricted information can be given to, or that we should increase the number of bodies to whom it cannot be given?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0664P0-06451'>
        <a name='S5LV0664P0_20040913_GCR_125'>  </a>
