      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-06537'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0664P0_20040913_GCR_211' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Clause 199 [<span class="italic">Investigation by the Board of complaints of maladministration</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-06538'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0664P0_20040913_GCR_212' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Baroness Hollis of Heigham</span> moved Amendment No. 277A:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-06539'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0664P0_20040913_GCR_213' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        Page 138, line 7, leave out from beginning to "or" and insert "the pension compensation provisions,"
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-06540'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0664P0_20040913_GCR_214' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
