      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-06569'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0664P0_20040913_GCR_243' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Lord Skelmersdale</span> moved Amendment No. 279:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-06570'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0664P0_20040913_GCR_244' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
