        Clause 210 [<span class="italic">Backdating the winding up of eligible schemes</span>]:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-06587'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S5LV0664P0_20040913_GCR_261' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="member">Baroness Hollis of Heigham</span> moved Amendments Nos. 279C to 279E:
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural' id='S5LV0664P0-06588'>
